<!---------------------- PHYSICAL CHARACTERISTICS -->|length={{convert|30|km|mi|abbr=on}}|width_min=|extra=}}Na '''Uciwai na Perfume''' ('''Sông Hương''' se '''Hương Giang'''; 香江) e dua na uciwai e takosova na siti o [[Huế]], ena loma ni yasana mai loma o Vietnam Thừa Thiên-Huế. Ena vula ikatakata, era lutu e wai na senikau mai na loga ni kau vuata mai na Huế, ka solia ki na uciwai e dua na aroma dau vaka na ibulibuli, ka sa mai vaka na ivakasaqa.<ref name="Vietnam beauty 2008">{{cite web|title=Perfume River (Hương River)|website=Vietnam beauty|date=August 28, 2008|url=http://www.vietnam-beauty.com/cities/hue/29-hue/66-perfume-river-hng-river.html|access-date=July 16, 2019}}</ref>

== iVurevure kei na drodro ==
E rua tiko na ivurevure ni Uciwai na Perfume; rau tekivu ruarua ena veiulunivanua o Dãy Trường Sơn veiulunivanua ka sota ena Bằng Lãng Fork. Na Tả Trạch (imawi lailai) e tekivu mai na veiulunivanua Trường Đồng ka drodro yani ki na vualiku ki na iqaqi. Sa qai drodro yani na uciwai ki na ceva ki na vualiku ka sivita na veivaletabu mai Hron Chén kei na Ngọc Trản, ka drodro yani ki na vualiku, me vakasauri ena Nguyệt Biều kei na bucabuca o Luong Bour. Me tomani tikoga, na Sông Hương (Uciwai Hương) sa drodro yani ki na vua-i-tokalau ki na Huế ka lako sivita na ivakadei ni Nguyễn na tui. E tomani tikoga na uciwai, ka siviti Hen islet kei na veikoro lelevu, ka takosova na ivovo ni Sinh (koroturaga makawa o Châu Hóa) ni bera ni ra curu yani ki na vanua o Kinani Giang.

Mai na Bằng Lãng ki na Thuan An estuary, na uciwai e 30 na kilomita na kena balavu ka cici vakamalua sara (me vaka ni sega soti ni sivia na wasawasa na uciwai). E butobuto na uciwai ni cagi voli ena yava ni Ngọc Trản ulunivanua, na vanua sa titobu kina na kena titobu. Na beseni ni Uciwai na Uciwai e levu duadua na uciwai mai Vietnam.<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Giang|title=Toward rainfall prediction by machine learning in Perfume River Basin, Thua Thien Hue Province, Vietnam|language=en|url=https://doi.org/10.1515/geo-2020-0276|doi=10.1515/geo-2020-0276|pages=963–976|issue=1|volume=13|date=1 January 2021|journal=Open Geosciences|first6=Hoang Ngo Tu|first1=Nguyen Hong|last6=Do|first5=Le Anh|last5=Phuong|first4=Quan Thanh|last4=Tho|first3=Tran Dinh|last3=Hieu|first2=YuRen|last2=Wang|issn=2391-5447}}</ref>

